<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Denemeler | İçerik Yönetim Sistemi</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #6366f1;
      --secondary: #a5b4fc;
      --accent: #fbbf24;
      --bg: #f8fafc;
      --text: #1e293b;
      --card-bg: #fff;
      --shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(99,102,241,0.10);
      --radius: 1.5rem;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .navbar {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
      padding: 1.2rem 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
      animation: fadeInDown 1s;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .navbar .brand {
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--primary);
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-right: 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .navbar .menu {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .navbar .menu a {
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      transition: color 0.2s;
      position: relative;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    }
    .navbar .menu a::after {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--primary);
      transition: width 0.3s;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .navbar .menu a:hover {
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    .navbar .menu a:hover::after {
      width: 100%;
    }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .navbar {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
      }
      .navbar .menu {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
      }
      .navbar .brand {
        margin-right: 0;
      }
    }
    .hero-header {
      width: 100vw;
      margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6366f1 60%, #a5b4fc 100%);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 1rem 2rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 0 0 2rem 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(99,102,241,0.10);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      animation: fadeInDown 1s;
    }
    .hero-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }
    .hero-header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #e0e7ef;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .exams-section {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
    .exam-card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 2.2rem 2rem 2rem 2rem;
      flex: 1 1 320px;
      max-width: 350px;
      min-width: 270px;
      text-align: left;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.2rem;
      position: relative;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      animation: fadeInUp 1s;
    }
    .exam-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.03);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(99,102,241,0.12);
    }
    .exam-icon {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .exam-title {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
      color: var(--primary);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .exam-desc {
      color: #555;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .badge {
      background: var(--secondary);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      padding: 0.3em 1em;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .exam-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 0.7rem;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 1.2rem;
      padding: 0.7rem 1.7rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(99,102,241,0.10);
    }
    .exam-link:hover {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .exams-section { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
    }
    @keyframes fadeInDown {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-40px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="navbar">
    <a href="/" class="brand"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> İçerik Yönetim Sistemi</a>
    <nav class="menu">
      <a href="/">Ana Sayfa</a>
      <a href="/dersler">Dersler</a>
      <a href="/katilimcilar">Katılımcılar</a>
      <a href="/denemeler">Denemeler</a>
      <a href="/hakkimda">Hakkımda</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-header">
    <h1>Denemeler</h1>
    <p>Her derse özel 15 soruluk denemelerle bilginizi test edin ve başarı sıralamanızı görün.</p>
  </div>
  <section class="exams-section">
    <div class="exam-card">
      <div class="exam-icon"><i class="fas fa-code"></i></div>
      <div class="exam-title">Web Programlama</div>
      <div class="exam-desc">HTML, CSS, JavaScript ve modern web teknolojileriyle ilgili 15 soruluk deneme.</div>
      <span class="badge">15 Soru</span>
      <a href="/denemeler/web-programlama/giris" class="exam-link">Başla</a>
    </div>
    <div class="exam-card">
      <div class="exam-icon"><i class="fas fa-database"></i></div>
      <div class="exam-title">Veritabanı Yönetimi</div>
      <div class="exam-desc">Veritabanı tasarımı, SQL ve yönetimiyle ilgili 15 soruluk deneme.</div>
      <span class="badge">15 Soru</span>
      <a href="/denemeler/veritabani/giris" class="exam-link">Başla</a>
    </div>
    <div class="exam-card">
      <div class="exam-icon"><i class="fas fa-server"></i></div>
      <div class="exam-title">Backend Geliştirme</div>
      <div class="exam-desc">Node.js, API, sunucu ve backend teknolojileriyle ilgili 15 soruluk deneme.</div>
      <span class="badge">15 Soru</span>
      <a href="/denemeler/backend" class="exam-link">Başla</a>
    </div>
    <div class="exam-card">
      <div class="exam-icon"><i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i></div>
      <div class="exam-title">Frontend Frameworks</div>
      <div class="exam-desc">React, Vue, Angular ve modern frontend framework'leriyle ilgili 15 soruluk deneme.</div>
      <span class="badge">15 Soru</span>
      <a href="/denemeler/frontend" class="exam-link">Başla</a>
    </div>
    <div class="exam-card">
      <div class="exam-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i></div>
      <div class="exam-title">Güvenlik ve DevOps</div>
      <div class="exam-desc">Siber güvenlik, DevOps ve otomasyon süreçleriyle ilgili 15 soruluk deneme.</div>
      <span class="badge">15 Soru</span>
      <a href="/denemeler/guvenlik-devops" class="exam-link">Başla</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>